0.8.name: wordpress/wordpress-wiki
0.8.description:
Tired of using Media Wiki? Sick of fighting with WordPress to get your own documentation project happening?

WordPress Wiki Plugin is the answer for you!

The new WordPress Wiki plugin made by the guys at Instinct (who brought you the famous Wordpress e-Commerce Plugin) have developed a new plugin that adds Wiki functionality to your WordPress powered website.
